observations.recommendation:
We reiterated our recommendation that the Municipal Mayor instruct the:

a. Municipal Accountant to exert effort in providing the breakdown or details of the recorded lot amounting to P1,702,275.75;

b. Appraisal Committee to continue the valuation of the unrecorded lands, titled and untitled, which will be used as the basis of the Municipal Accountant in recording the parcels of land/adjusting the Land account balance;

c. OIC-Municipal Assessor to verify the ownership of the lots named under the Municipality per its tax declarations but were not supported with certificate of titles; and

d. OIC-Municipal Assessor to continue the titling of the all untitled lots found to be owned by the Municipality and to make the necessary follow-ups to concerned agencies to avoid third party claims and land disputes in the future.

We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:
(e instruct the Municipal Accountant to provide for the breakdown or details of the Municipal land unidentified recorded of P1,473,275.75; 
(¢) instruct the Municipal Treasurer/Municipal Assessor in locating documents to establish the amount and mode of acquisition of the unrecorded lots titled in the name of the Municipality or prioritize the creation of the Appraisal Committee for the valuation of the unrecorded lands, titled and untitled, which will be used as the basis of the Municipal Accountant in recording the parcels of land/adjusting the Land account balance;
* instruct the MBO 1o provide the budget for the processing of the land titles; and
* require the Municipal Assessor/designated person to facilitate the titling of the untitled parcels of land.

We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:
instruct the Municipal Accountant to provide for the breakdown or details of the unidentified recorded land of P1,473,275.75;
instruct the Municipal Treasurer/Municipal Assessor in locating documents to establish the amount and mode of acquisition of the 16 unrecorded lots or prioritize the creation of the Appraisal Committee for the valuation of the unrecorded lands, titled and untitled, which will be used as the basis of the Municipal Accountant in recording the parcels of land/adjusting the Land account balance;
instruct the MBO to provide the budget for the processing of the land titles; and
require the Municipal Assessor/designated person to facilitate the titling of the untitled parcels of land.
